'''{{zy|創|chuāng|ㄔㄨㄤ}}伤性脑损伤'''又稱'''腦外傷'''，是指外力对大脑造成的损伤<ref>{{Cite web|title=Basic Information about Traumatic Brain Injury {{!}} Concussion {{!}} Traumatic Brain Injury {{!}} CDC Injury Center|url=https://www.cdc.gov/traumaticbraininjury/basics.html|accessdate=2020-07-21|date=2019-03-06|work=www.cdc.gov|language=en-us|archive-date=2021-05-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210514104756/https://www.cdc.gov/traumaticbraininjury/basics.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。造成创伤性脑损伤的原因包括[[跌倒|跌倒]]、[[車禍|車禍]]和暴力。大腦受伤后的腦內各种狀況還有可能会导致大腦损伤更為嚴重。在世界范围内的儿童和青少年中，创伤性脑损伤是導致死亡和残疾的主要原因<ref name="Clark01">{{Cite book|title=Brain injury|publisher=Kluwer Academic Publishers|location=Boston|year=2001|isbn=978-0-7923-7532-6|chapterurl=https://books.google.com/books?id=uRR4jKhF_iUC&pg=PA1|page=1|access-date=2021-02-22|archive-date=2020-08-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200820000925/https://books.google.com/books?id=uRR4jKhF_iUC&pg=PA1|dead-url=no}}</ref>。男性遭受脑外伤的频率约为女性的两倍<ref name="RaoLyketsos">{{Cite journal|title=Neuropsychiatric sequelae of traumatic brain Injury|journal=Psychosomatics|issue=2|doi=10.1176/appi.psy.41.2.95|year=2000|volume=41|pages=95–103|pmid=10749946}}</ref>。用于诊断创伤性脑损伤的成像技术有[[X射线计算机断层成像|X射线计算机断层成像]]（CT）和[[核磁共振成像|核磁共振成像]]（MRI）。创伤性脑损伤的预防措施包括繫好[[座位安全帶|安全带]]、戴好头盔、不饮酒驾驶、老年人的防跌倒保護工作和儿童的安全保護措施<ref name="CDC2019Pre">{{Cite web|title=Prevention|url=https://www.cdc.gov/traumaticbraininjury/prevention.html|accessdate=May 28, 2019|date=March 4, 2019|work=CDC|language=en-us|archive-date=2021-06-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210616082432/https://www.cdc.gov/traumaticbraininjury/prevention.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。根据大腦受伤情况，治疗手段包括药物治療、紧急手术或數年后的手术等措施。康复手段包括[[物理治疗|物理治疗]]、[[言语治疗|言语治疗]]、[[休閒治療|休閒治療]]、[[職能治療|職能治療]]等手段。

